description: Lance has always had a passion for grilling food. Whether at home grilling for family and friends or at group gatherings and charity events, he has a knack and a flair for great tasting gourmet meals.Our concept is healthy eating without losing the great flavor or taste that brings everyone to the table. No frying, no microwave ovens and we don’t char our food. Fresh cooked food when you order. We buy organic when we can and local when available. So, come join us and Get Addicted!
name: Grilled Addiction
